程序包 util.Video

类 JavaFX_MediaPlayer

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
util.Video.JavaFX_MediaPlayer
public class JavaFX_MediaPlayer
extends javafx.application.Application

Class JavaFX_MediaPlayerVideo Player Based On JavaFX.

Accepts a String representing the video path.
return Long representing the watching time.
Base on JavaFX components such as MediaView MediaPlayer.
Satisfy thread security.

版本:
V1.0
作者:
Zhanao Zhang
